      .row
        .col-md-12
          h2 About the Afropolymath          
          p I'm Chidiebere I Nnadi and I graduated with an degree in EE from 
            a(href="http://covenantuniversity.edu.ng") this school
            |  in 2012. I have been writing code for the web since 2007 but only started seriously building products in 2010. I consider myself a Full Stack Web Developer and I have worked with several programming languages including Python, PHP, Javascript, Java and very little Perl.          
          p I currently teach Software Development at 
            a(href="http://andela.com") Andela
            |  here in Lagos, Nigeria.            
          p In my spare time I enjoy listening to good music and just thinking about crazy ideas.            
          h2 Stack Update (As at 17.04.2016)         
          p TLDR Version - Currently still learning Python. Using web application frameworks like Django and Flask. Playing around with lots of Python Tools (Will share my best links soon. There are so many!). For infrastructure, I'm still using Amazon AWS for real work and Heroku for smaller projects (Like this site). For Databases I'm using PostgreSQL, Firebase and Redis. FrontEnd is a serious issue right now. Sticking to Angular 1.X for mission critical stuff but learning ReactJS and VueJS. Using Semantic UI for web components, Bootstrap and Flexgrid for Grid and Layouts, and building everything else from scratch.  
          p At the heart of my development is my pencil, sketchbook and Photoshop which I make use of for prototyping.         
          p Click here to view the latest Stack Update post  
